    "summary": "Ik heb ook een Nederlandstalige CV die ik op aanvraag graag toestuur.\n\nFor a graduate student Forest and Nature Conservation, I have much knowledge, experience and motivation thanks to my great interest in nature. I am interested in ecology, management, policy, social issues and their integration. In my free time I have studied wild plants since many years and I have organised many activities for the Nederlandse Jeugdbond voor Natuurstudie. I am dedicated, like teamwork and can communicate and organise well. I like to share knowledge through writing, presenting and leading excursions.\n\nI would like to work for an organisation that manages natural areas or advises about the management of such areas. Further I am interested in working for government agencies and research institutes. I prefer to work in the Netherlands, Germany or maybe another European country.\n\nI hope to contribute to the conservation, restoration and sustainable management of natural areas. I care about biodiversity, natural processes and landscape quality. The connection between people and nature is important to me. Therefore I would also like to engage in education, sustainable use of nature and involvement of stakeholders in nature management.",
